
# 📊 Project 06 — Sentiment Analysis (NLP)

This project implements an end-to-end sentiment analysis system using classical Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques.

It converts raw customer text into numerical features using TF-IDF and classifies sentiment using Logistic Regression.

The system is designed to be simple, reusable, and suitable for real-world deployment.

---

## 🚀 Project Objectives

- Clean and preprocess raw text data
- Convert text into TF-IDF vectors
- Train a Logistic Regression classifier
- Evaluate model performance using F1-score
- Save a reusable prediction pipeline
- Enable sentiment prediction on new input text

