## 📊 Dataset

A small, manually labeled dataset is created for demonstration purposes.

### Sample Data

| Text Example                                | Label |
|--------------------------------------------|--------|
| This product is amazing and works perfectly | 1 |
| Terrible experience, completely useless    | 0 |
| I love this, would buy again                | 1 |
| Worst purchase I have ever made             | 0 |

### Label Encoding

| Value | Meaning  |
|-------|----------|
| 1     | Positive |
| 0     | Negative |

The dataset simulates real customer feedback and allows focus on building NLP pipelines.

