## ⚙️ Machine Learning Pipeline

The project uses a Scikit-learn Pipeline to ensure consistent preprocessing and modeling.

### Pipeline Steps

1. TF-IDF Vectorization  
2. Logistic Regression Classification  

```

Text → TF-IDF → Logistic Regression → Prediction

```

### TF-IDF Configuration

- Lowercasing enabled
- English stopwords removed
- Vocabulary size limited
- Optional n-gram support

### Model

- Logistic Regression
- Maximum iterations: 1000+
- Balanced training

---

## 📈 Model Training

- Dataset split: 80% training, 20% testing
- Stratified sampling applied
- Same pipeline used for training and inference

This ensures fair evaluation and prevents data leakage.

---

